NAME
    MojoX::Session::Store::File - File store for MojoX::Session

SYNOPSIS
        my $session = MojoX::Session->new(
            store => MojoX::Session::Store::File->new,
        );

ATTRIBUTES
    MojoX::Session::Store::File implemets the following attributes:

  dir
    Directory to store session files. Must be writable. Defaults to your OS
    temp directory.

  prefix
    String to prefix each session filename. Defaults to "mojoxsess".

  driver
    Module to serialize your session data. Default is Storable. FreezeThaw
    also comes with this package. You are welcome to add your own (see
    MojoX::Session::Store::File::Driver).

METHODS
    MojoX::Session::Store::File inherits all methods from
    MojoX::Session::Store.

CONTRIBUTE
